  "title": "Craft Beer Tour in Miraflores",
  "description": "With this experience they will be able to enjoy and taste the best craft beers made in different parts of Peru; We will start at the original brewery in Cusco, then we will go to one in Ancash and end at one in Lima, which is the most important brewery in the country.\n\nThey will taste more than 14 beers on tap and identify the differences that exist between each of them according to the origin of each production, style and supplies.\n\nAt the end they will try an aperitif.",
  "all_descriptions": [
    "With this experience they will be able to enjoy and taste the best craft beers made in different parts of Peru; We will start at the original brewery in Cusco, then we will go to one in Ancash and end at one in Lima, which is the most important brewery in the country.\n\nThey will taste more than 14 beers on tap and identify the differences that exist between each of them according to the origin of each production, style and supplies.\n\nAt the end they will try an aperitif.",
    "ItineraryEnjoy Peruvian craft beers\n\n\"The tour includes beers\"\n\nFirst:\nWe will meet in the Miraflores district (the name of the reservation and the address of the first bar will be sent to you when you purchase the experience)\n\nWhat will we do:\nWe will visit 3 Peruvian breweries that belong to different cities of the country where we will be able to identify the difference in flavors during the tour due to the inputs belonging to each region, in this way they will be able to taste unique flavors of beer styles in each establishment.\nAt the moment these types of craft beers are not being exported, therefore, they can only be tasted in Peru.\n\nIn these bars you can taste the most important beers in the Country:\n\n*First Stop: We will meet and drink - 1 beer, I will recommend it according to your knowledge and/or tastes.\n*Second Stop: We will taste 4 beers with flavors of inputs from the Inca culture.\n*Third Stop: We will return to Lima and taste 4 beers with shades of different flavors and styles.\nImportant fact:\nAll additional consumptions that do not include those mentioned above will be assumed by you.",
    "C. Manuel Bonilla 100, Miraflores 15074, PeruI will send the address of the first bar where we will meet.\nThese bars are very close to Kennedy Park",
    "End:This activity ends back at the meeting point."
